overview: From their tour for THE HUMAN FACTOR, this is Metal Church's performance at Dynamo Open Air 1991 (at Kunstijsbaan, Eindhoven, Netherlands), on May 20. Setlist: 01 - Beyond the Black - 02 - The Human Factor - 03 - In Mourning - 04 - Fake Healer - 05 - Flee from Reality - 06 - In Harm's Way - 07 - Ton of Bricks - 08 - Start the Fire - 09 - The Final Word - 10 - Agent Green - 11 - Date with Poverty - 12 - Metal Church.  Lineup:  Mike Howe (vocals), John Marshall (guitars), Craig Wells (guitars), Duke Erickson (bass),  Kirk Arrington (drums).
title: Metal Church Dynamo Classic Concerts 1991
